public interface MapReducePlugin<T extends Atom,S extends MolSetInterface>
extends AnalysisPluginInterface

An abstracted map-reduce interface. These interfaces will eventually restrict our plug-ins. Currently, they are just placeholders. Implementation orients itself on HBase's TableMapper, TableReduce.
